{"tid":1212041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾200特首選委晚上聯署要求林鄭月娥下台","createTime":"2019-06-12T17:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:25:00.000Z","uid":22556,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ccee26f842fbd489579841f995b0a0cd17216f0d","tid":1212041,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:11:08.000Z","msg":"2017年3月26日，林鄭月娥以777票當選第五屆行政長官。208名選委參與聯署，佔有份投票選特首的1200名選委約百分之十七，包括黎廣德、張銳輝、張達明、查錫我、梁家傑和潘熙等，要求林鄭月娥下台、停止警方暴力及撤回逃犯修例。<br />\n<br />\n他們批評，林鄭月娥漠視民意、不願撤回《逃犯條例》修訂，今日因政府的冷漠引發民眾自發的佔領運動，卻遭到警方暴力清場，較當年雨傘運動以更暴力方式對待示威者，認為林鄭月娥已盡失其正當性，必須引咎下台，並重新改選新任特首。<br />\n<br />\n聯署名單如下 ：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190612/s00001/1560354007895/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e9%80%be200%e7%89%b9%e9%a6%96%e9%81%b8%e5%a7%94%e8%81%af%e7%bd%b2%e8%a6%81%e6%b1%82%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad%e6%9c%88%e5%a8%a5%e4%b8%8b%e5%8f%b0-%e9%87%8d%e6%96%b0%e9%81%b8%e7%89%b9%e9%a6%96%ef%bc%88%e9%99%84%e5%90%8d%e5%96%ae%ef%bc%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190612%2Fs00001%2F1560354007895%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%2580%25be200%25e7%2589%25b9%25e9%25a6%2596%25e9%2581%25b8%25e5%25a7%2594%25e8%2581%25af%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e8%25a6%2581%25e6%25b1%2582%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad%25e6%259c%2588%25e5%25a8%25a5%25e4%25b8%258b%25e5%258f%25b0-%25e9%2587%258d%25e6%2596%25b0%25e9%2581%25b8%25e7%2589%25b9%25e9%25a6%2596%25ef%25bc%2588%25e9%2599%2584%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%2596%25ae%25ef%25bc%2589&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=b89d954a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190612%2Fs00001%2F1560354007895%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%2580%25be200%25e7%2589%25b9%25e